# ğŸ•¸ï¸ Araxia

**Araxia** is a lightweight, customizable time series forecasting model tailored for structured datasets like grocery store sales. Inspired by the structure of spider webs and powered by neural networks, Araxia makes forecasting intuitive, modular, and fun.

> â€œPattern is the web. Prediction is the spider.â€ â€” *Araxia Philosophy*

---

## ğŸ§  Features

- ğŸ” Lagged features with flexible windowing
- ğŸ“… Time-aware feature engineering (cyclic time, dates, day-of-week)
- ğŸ•¸ï¸ Neural network forecaster (built with NumPy from scratch)
- ğŸ§ª Easy backtesting on training data
- ğŸ“ˆ Built-in plot support for forecasts
- ğŸ§© Modular: plug in your own preprocessing or model layers
- âœ… Lightweight with no heavy dependencies

